	<h1 class="title">如果你去纽约，不妨尝尝华尔道夫酒店顶楼那些蜜蜂酿的蜜</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">David Graver</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-30 08:10:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15606/medium/15606.jpg?1443353758" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="15606" data-title="《如果你去纽约，不妨尝尝华尔道夫酒店顶楼那些蜜蜂酿的蜜》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15606/medium/15606.jpg?1443353758" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15606.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
